org.catacombae.jfuse
Interface FUSEErrorValues

All Known Subinterfaces:
FUSE26FileSystem, FUSE26Operations, FUSEFileSystem
All Known Implementing Classes:
FUSE26FileSystemAdapter, FUSE26Test.Yada, FUSEFileSystemAdapter, HelloFS
public interface FUSEErrorValues

Manual enumeration of all thinkable errno constants that could be returned by FUSE. The list of constants is based on the Darwin (Mac OS X) errno.h, but other constants can be added later if they are needed. (These are probably enough)
Note that the actual values of the constants don't mean anything, except that all are positive, and should be returned in negative form (ex. "return -ENOENT;").

Author:
Erik Larsson
